VALUES ('Cinematic Tropical Lagoon Travel Editorial Portrait', 'A highly structured JSON prompt designed to generate a cinematic, photorealistic travel editorial portrait of a woman on the bow of a wooden longtail boat in a tropical lagoon. The prompt meticulously details the scene, including the turquoise water, limestone cliffs, the subject''s pose, wardrobe (soft pastel pink knit mini dress), lighting (strong midday sun), and strict constraints regarding text and realism.', '{
