2 景深：背景虚化很弱或几乎无纹理，主体更突出
3 氛围：甜美感女团韩杂风写真，甜美可爱、精致梦幻、轻微玻璃质感光泽', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G_aUWD4WMAA1YHU.jpg","https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G_aUWDTbMAA7alq.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/qisi_ai/status/2014961007068905955", "sourcePublishedAt": "2026-01-24T07:18:34.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"\u9a91\u53f8Chase\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/qisi_ai\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
