VALUES ('Hyper-Real Macro Studio Shot of a LEGO Technic Kitbash', 'This prompt is designed to transform a subject (Nikola Tesla, in this case) into a hyper-realistic macro studio product shot of a LEGO Technic-style mechanical kitbash. It includes detailed instructions on zone mapping for construction, mechanism logic, and specific photo rules for a studio aesthetic, emphasizing shallow depth of field and realistic plastic textures.', 'Nikola Tesla -> System Instruction: Edit {argument name="subject" default="Nikola Tesla"} into a hyper-real macro studio product shot of a LEGO Technic-style kitbash doing a clever pose

