VALUES ('Infographic Prompt Template for Objects', 'A reusable prompt template for Nano Banana Pro designed to create an infographic image of a generic object. The prompt instructs the AI to combine a photorealistic render of the object with technical annotation overlays, using black ink line drawings, labels, measurements, and schematic diagrams on a pure white background, aiming for an educational, engineering-manual aesthetic. This is a generalized version of the previous prompt.', '“Create an infographic image of [{argument name="object" default="OBJECT"}], combining a realistic photograph or photoreal render of the object with technical annotation overlays placed directly on top.

