Output:
1080×1080, ultra-crisp, social-feed optimized, no watermark.”', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G_Yj8SGX0AAa9YM.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/brightcoding/status/2014837408374706372", "sourcePublishedAt": "2026-01-23T23:07:26.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Mohamed IDBRAHIM\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/brightcoding\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
