VALUES ('Cinematic Winter Street Fashion Prompt', 'A detailed cinematic prompt for generating a winter street fashion photograph during a light snowfall. It features a woman stepping out of an olive green car, wearing a gray knit dress and oversized herringbone coat, emphasizing textures, analog film aesthetic (Kodak Portra 400), and a nostalgic European city atmosphere.', 'A photograph taken during a light snowfall of a young adult woman with soft, medium-length, wavy blonde hair, slightly tousled by the wind, a face with natural makeup without heavy make-up, softly lit and partially turned to the side, a slender figure, and an elegant pose, stepping out of an old olive green car. She is wearing a cozy light gray knit midi-length sheath dress with a knee-length slit, over an oversized gray herringbone wool coat, cinched at the waist with a wide brown leather belt-a classic, minimalist street style. Accessories: A small horse-shaped jewelry brooch adorned with ruby stones is pinned to the coat, black leather gloves, a large soft black leather tote bag, and a chunky gold ring on one hand worn over the glove. A natural cedar branch, a sprig with red berries, and the edge of a wrapped Christmas present are visible from the open bag. The scene takes place on a snowy winter city street, with blurred buildings in muted tones creating a cinematic European atmosphere. The textures of the soft woolen yarn of the dress, the textured wool coat, the smooth leather of the gloves and bag, and the metal parts of the car create a sense of the coming New Year. The architecture is decorated in the minimalist style of German cities. The lighting is soft natural daylight with subtle shadows under a slightly overcast sky, creating a diffuse, cinematic glow. The mood is cozy, elegant, cinematic, slightly nostalgic, sophisticated, yet relaxed. The camera is positioned at waist level, looking up as if the viewer is standing at an open car door, with a medium shot capturing the upper body and part of the legs, focusing on the outfit and pose an the viewer exits the car. The style is analog film, with high grain and an editorial street fashion aesthetic, shot on Kodak Portla 400.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G_J8T0KW0AAYvhE.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/harboriis/status/2013808667821514759", "sourcePublishedAt": "2026-01-21T02:59:35.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Harboriis\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/harboriis\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
