VALUES ('Couture Cottagecore Fashion Editorial Prompt', 'A highly detailed prompt for generating an ultra-realistic, high-fashion editorial photograph of a woman in a ''Couture Cottagecore'' outfit (teal and gold bodice, mustard taffeta skirt) seated in a field of yellow wildflowers, emphasizing Golden Hour lighting and deep bokeh.', 'Using the uploaded image, Create an ultra-realistic, high-fashion editorial photograph of a stunning woman with long, flowing rich dark brown hair and striking blue or green eyes.

