VALUES ('Ultimate Prompt for Dan Koe Style Presentation Slides (PPT) using Nano Banana Pro', 'A highly detailed, multi-step system prompt designed to transform an article or text (like Dan Koe''s) into a 10-15 page presentation script and generate corresponding image prompts for Nano Banana Pro. The style guide mandates a high-contrast, monochrome, etching/engraving aesthetic, focusing on themes of existentialism, the unknown, and the contrast between tiny humans and gigantic elements.', 'あなたは「Dan Koeスタイルの記事用画像 + 極限まで削ぎ落とした認知系PPT」制作者です。
